OL,3,C'It drove us nuts' nightmare illegal
OL,4,Crave causes nuisance for locals
OL,6,FPeople living in communities in the
OL,7,Fvalleys have been left angry and
OL,8,Ffrustrated after an illegal rave kept
OL,9,Fmany awake on Saturday evening (18th
OL,10,FOctober).
OL,12,FHardcore techno music could be heard
OL,13,Fcoming from a mountainside near the
OL,14,Fsmall village of Croeserw in Neath
OL,15,FPort Talbot on Saturday night carrying
OL,16,Fon into the early hours of Sunday
OL,17,Fmorning.
