OL,3,C'It drove us nuts' nightmare illegal
OL,4,Crave causes nuisance for locals
OL,6,FThere are multiple reports on social
OL,7,Fmedia that people living in Cwmbach,
OL,8,FTreorchy, Abernant, Mountain Ash,
OL,9,FLandare, Cwmaman, Cwmdare and Aberdare
OL,10,Fheard the noise.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police remain in the area
OL,13,Fwhich they have described as the spot
OL,14,Ffor an "unlicensed music event."
OL,16,FIt is reported that some of the
OL,17,Fattendees to the rave came as far from
OL,18,FBristol. Locals who had to put up with
OL,19,Fthen noise have described the nuisance.
