OL,3,C'It drove us nuts' nightmare illegal
OL,4,Crave causes nuisance for locals
OL,6,FCatherine Currier said: "It started
OL,7,Fjust after midnight, I felt it before
OL,8,FI heard it! The noise drove us nuts
OL,9,Ffor hours and the dog was barking like
OL,10,Fcrazy.
OL,12,F"It sounded like a hardcore techno
OL,13,Frave coming from over the mountain
OL,14,Fsomewhere, or maybe the country park -
OL,15,Fnot sure. Think I must've got to sleep
OL,16,Fwell past 2am, with my earplugs in.
OL,17,FNightmare."
