OL,6,FA spokesperson for South Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Officers attended a report of
OL,8,Fan unlicensed music event taking place
OL,9,Fnear Croeserw last night.
OL,11,F"Officers remain at the location to
OL,12,Fensure the safe dispersal of attendees.
OL,14,F"Enquiries are on-going in relation to
OL,15,Fany criminal offences which may have
OL,16,Fbeen committed."
