OL,3,C'It drove us nuts' nightmare illegal
OL,4,Crave causes nuisance for locals
OL,6,FIt's not the first illegal rave held
OL,7,Fin Wales, which has seen people travel
OL,8,Ffrom across the UK. During the summer,
OL,9,Fa large gathering took place in a
OL,10,Fremote Ceredigion forest which led to
OL,11,Fconcerns for the environment and
OL,12,Fwildlife in the area.
OL,14,FIn August Dyfed Powys Police said due
OL,15,Fto the number of people there, they
OL,16,Fdecided to prioritise disrupting and
OL,17,Fstopping entry of any further vehicles
OL,18,Fand people under a Section 63 notice.
