OL,6,FIn June the force also had to break up
OL,7,Fan illegal rave in a forest in
OL,8,FBrechfa, Carmarthenshire.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said at the time:
OL,11,F"There is little doubt that these
OL,12,Ftypes of events are very well planned,
OL,13,Forganised and that local knowledge is
OL,14,Fimportant in drawing down the main
OL,15,Fgroup to a particular field, or area
OL,16,Fof land."
